\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Commercial Real Estate Vulnerability Across Monetary Policy Regimes. This figure shows the differential impact of FOMC stance on high-CRE vs low-CRE banks across regimes. The CRE sensitivity channel operates primarily during ZLB periods (Dovish\,$\times $\,ZLB\,$\times $\,CRE = +0.25, p = 0.013).}}{14}{figure.caption.9}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:cre}{{4}{14}{Commercial Real Estate Vulnerability Across Monetary Policy Regimes. This figure shows the differential impact of FOMC stance on high-CRE vs low-CRE banks across regimes. The CRE sensitivity channel operates primarily during ZLB periods (Dovish\,$\times $\,ZLB\,$\times $\,CRE = +0.25, p = 0.013)}{figure.caption.9}{}}
